      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to help this awesome car find its next home. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and still drives like a dream! It's super clean, runs great, and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes. You\u2019re going to love how it handles\u2014come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
