    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered chassis. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefitting from a recently calibrated dual-VANOS system and clean individual throttle body synchronization. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural weak point. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with healthy bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in and high-speed stability expected of an M-division product. A well-sorted driver's car with excellent mechanical vitals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
