    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a balanced blend of performance and comfort. The exterior presents beautifully, retaining a deep, glossy finish that catches the light, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood from normal road use. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and inviting space; the leather seats are firm and supportive, showing only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s entry point. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a fresh multi-point inspection already completed. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide a firm, confident feel. This is a dependable, well-cared-for car ready for its next chapter with a buyer who appreciates quality and transparency.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
